727436f-a.title: Queens: Mott Avenue - Redfern Avenue
727436f-a.text:
Mott Ave., at the N.W. corner of Redfern Ave., showing the Hotel
Montauk. Also shown is a branch line of the Long Island Railroad.
January 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
